name: Braidless Sew In Class
description:
The Braidless sew in is said to eliminate bulkiness throughout the hair, leave no lumps or bumps, and give more flexibility with styling as far as putting your hair in a nice updo style or high bun without visible extensions.  Women LOVEEEE it and it is becoming the most popular sew in ever!!! Last up to 4 months.  

Installation is Completely safe.

The cost of the class is $75. It requires a $25 deposit and the remaining$50 is due at the door.
